import FloatingLabel from 'react-bootstrap/FloatingLabel';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';

function JoinMembershipForm() {
    return (
        <>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="membershipinput">
                <Form.Check
                    inline
                    type="checkbox"
                    id="prospan"
                    label="Prospan"
                />
                <Form.Check
                    inline
                    type="checkbox"
                    id="viartril"
                    label="Viartril-S"
                />
            </Form.Group>

            <FloatingLabel
            controlId="nameinput"
            label="Name"
            className="mb-3">
                <Form.Control type="input" placeholder="Your name" />
            </FloatingLabel>

            <FloatingLabel
            controlId="emailinput"
            label="Email address"
            className="mb-3">
                <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="name@example.com" />
            </FloatingLabel>

            <FloatingLabel
            controlId="contactinput"
            label="Contact number"
            className="mb-3">
                <Form.Control type="input" placeholder="Your contact" />
            </FloatingLabel>

            <Row className="g-2">
                <Col md>
                    <FloatingLabel
                    controlId="blockinput"
                    label="House / Block number"
                    className="mb-3">
                        <Form.Control type="input" placeholder="House / Block number" />
                    </FloatingLabel>
                </Col>
                <Col md>
                    <FloatingLabel
                    controlId="streetinput"
                    label="Street"
                    className="mb-3">
                        <Form.Control type="input" placeholder="Street" />
                    </FloatingLabel>
                </Col>
            </Row>

            <Row className="g-2">
                <Col md>
                    <FloatingLabel
                    controlId="unitinput"
                    label="Unit number"
                    className="mb-3">
                        <Form.Control type="input" placeholder="Unit number" />
                    </FloatingLabel>
                </Col>
                <Col md>
                    <FloatingLabel
                    controlId="postalinput"
                    label="Postcal Code"
                    className="mb-3">
                        <Form.Control type="input" placeholder="Postal Code" />
                    </FloatingLabel>
                </Col>
            </Row>

            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="declarationinput">
                <Form.Label>Declaration</Form.Label>
                <Form.Check
                    inline
                    type="checkbox"
                    id="declaration"
                    label="I agree that I have read the Personal Data Privacy Statement and consent to the given information being used by PHARMLINE to contact me about membership."
                />
            </Form.Group>
        </>
    );
}

export default JoinMembershipForm;
